    "Note that whether ωgc < or > ωc pi depends on the actual, but unknown, gain conditions of G(jω).",
    "The largest of both appears crucial for a stable T i assignment.",
    "Following to that, the tuning ruleT i = 10 max ωgc, ωc pi (3)is suggested for the integrator time constant.",
    "Note that the multiplicative factor ten corresponds to one decade of shifting back (i.e.",
    "to the left in frequency range) the phase advance of C(jω)."
